\pard\f0\fs28  ({\b a}) Subsp. {\b padus}: Tree up to 17 m; young shoots glabrescent; leaves glabrous beneath, or with hairs only in axils of veins; racemes more or less pendent; flowers with heavy scent.{\i  Throughout the range of the species}.
